								<div class="title" id="post-title-3592930">
																		
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/boogey-man23" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2362395); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2362395&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610163883" alt="Boogey_Man23" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2362395)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/boogey-man23" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2362395); return false;" >Boogey_Man23</a></span> <span class="odate time_1505461366 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">15 Sep 2017 07:42</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3592930">
									

<p>Hi, thanks for reading! Your comment is understandable.</p>
<p>I'm afraid this tale does pretty much rely on the reader following the cross-link to the relevant SCP (near the end of the first section) in order to make the events transparent.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoiler-y&nbsp;excerpt&nbsp;and&nbsp;explanation</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoiler-y&nbsp;excerpt&nbsp;and&nbsp;explanation</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>For the record, <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-1087">that relevant SCP is 1087.</a></p>
<p>From its <em>Description</em>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>SCP-1087's saliva contains an unknown chemical [&#8230;] once it makes contact with a mammalian bloodstream, it travels to the subject's exocrine glands and alters their biochemical functions. This results in affected subjects producing and secreting a pheromone designated as SCP-1087-1.</p>
<p>Mammals coming into contact with SCP-1087-1 become increasingly agitated, specifically towards the being emitting the pheromone. As time passes, the concentration of pheromones will severely hamper the judgment of nearby animals, including humans, compelling all mammals near the affected subject to hunt and attack the organism emitting SCP-1087-1.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This pretty well sums up what took place that night (with the lost camper as the 'affected subject').</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>One suggestion I received was to present some of that (unredacted) description itself right in the tale, perhaps at the line break in between the two sections, but ultimately I decided not to. I wonder now if maybe I should try that, or if there's possibly a better way to present the crosslink.</p>

							</div>

								
					
